  <text x="20" y="32" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">India's crypto reporting gap — from 39 million to one in four</text>
  <g font-family="sans-serif">
    <rect x="20" y="58" width="640" height="54" rx="8" fill="#1c1c1f" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <text x="40" y="80" fill="#38bdf8" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Total crypto investors</text>
    <text x="660" y="80" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end">~39 million</text>
    <text x="40" y="100" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12">Of ~1.5 billion population · ~$2.1B held as of May</text>

    <rect x="90" y="140" width="490" height="54" rx="8" fill="#1c1c1f" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <text x="110" y="162" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Actual transactors, FY ending Mar '23</text>
    <text x="560" y="162" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end">645,000</text>
    <text x="110" y="182" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12">Fiscal year ending March 2023</text>

    <rect x="180" y="222" width="310" height="54" rx="8" fill="#1c1c1f" stroke="#fb7185" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <text x="200" y="244" fill="#fb7185" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Disclosed on tax returns</text>
    <text x="470" y="244" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end">Under 1 in 4</text>
    <text x="200" y="264" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12">The rest sit outside the tax office's view</text>

    <line x1="340" y1="112" x2="340" y2="138" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arG1e)"/>
    <line x1="340" y1="194" x2="340" y2="220" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arG1e)"/>
    <defs><marker id="arG1e" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L6,3 L0,6 Z" fill="#71717a"/></marker></defs>

    <rect x="20" y="308" width="640" height="86" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#71717a" stroke-width="1"/>
    <text x="340" y="334" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">Despite a 30% flat tax and 1% TDS — among the world's harshest —</text>
    <text x="340" y="356" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">offshore exchanges, private wallets and P2P trades stay off the radar</text>
    <text x="340" y="378" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700">RBI's view: blocking banks is more certain than taxing</text>
  </g>
  <text x="350" y="410" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Sources: Indian government documents reviewed by Reuters, CoinDesk (July 8, 2026) · as of reporting time</text>
</svg>
</div>
